comment: Oladipo (OKC) makes marginal contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his SQBR on the drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) sets the screen on Roberson (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] RATR shows that Gibson (OKC) never fully clears the lane and is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Gibson (OKC) obtains a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area prior to the contact with Nurkic (POR) on his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, Gibson (OKC) was not in the restricted area and the ruling on the floor of an offensive foul on Nurkic (POR) is confirmed.
Kanter (OKC) sets the screen on Crabbe (POR) and absorbs the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] RATR shows McCollum (POR) move his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Nurkic (POR) firms up his position and sets the screen on Roberson (OKC).
